# ovh_vps_veeam_restore_points (Data Source)

Use this data source to list available Veeam restore point IDs for a VPS.

## Example Usage

```hcl
data "ovh_vps_veeam_restore_points" "points" {
  service_name = "vps-xxxxxx.vps.ovh.net"
}

data "ovh_vps_veeam_restore_points" "recent" {
  service_name  = "vps-xxxxxx.vps.ovh.net"
  creation_time = "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}
```

## Argument Reference

* `service_name` - (Required) The internal name of your VPS.
* `creation_time` - (Optional) Filter restore points by creation time (RFC3339).

## Attributes Reference

* `result` - List of Veeam restore point IDs.
